						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							The Brown-throated lives from Honduras in the north, through Nicaragua, Costa Rica, and Panama, into Venezuela, Colombia, Ecuador, Bolivia and eastern Peru. It is absent from the Amazon region and east of the Rio Negro.
						</text>
